ActFisheries Act
Oceans Act
Coastal Fisheries Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Department of Fisheries and Oceans Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN DEPARTMENT OF FISHERIES AND OCEANS REGULATIONS (Miscellaneous Program) in order to (1) ensure that the regulations are clear, accurate, and serve to minimize the possibility of misinterpretation; (2) update the regulations to reflect current terminology and remove any outdated references; and (3) respond to recommendations made by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
